<h3>Strategy</h3>
<p>Bingo is largely a game of chance, but players can improve their odds by using multiple cards and paying close attention to the numbers called. Quick recognition and marking can make a difference in close games.</p>
<p>Its simplicity and reliance on luck make Bingo an entertaining and accessible game for players of all ages.</p>
